37:55.270 --> 37:57.511
It's funny how we have a word
for that concept,

37:57.600 --> 38:00.012
but there's no way we can understand it.

38:02.530 --> 38:03.599
Maybe love.

38:06.030 --> 38:07.145
Love?

38:07.910 --> 38:10.822
Maybe love is how you understand infinity.

38:11.910 --> 38:14.652
When your love has no limits,
when it goes on forever.

38:15.080 --> 38:17.241
Maybe that feels like infinity.

38:23.380 --> 38:24.199
