38:35.600 --> 38:38.842
[chuckles] I feel fucking great.

38:38.940 --> 38:40.805
[both laugh]

38:40.900 --> 38:43.812
At this moment,
I am not afraid of anything.

38:43.900 --> 38:46.232
-I am fearless.
-Yeah.

38:49.450 --> 38:50.269
