were gonna fucking leave me behind?

43:11.460 --> 43:15.044
-That's messed up, Alex. It's messed up.
-I'm sorry.

43:16.510 --> 43:18.660
Everybody here loves you.

43:20.220 --> 43:21.289
And you just don't care?

43:21.390 --> 43:24.382
I do care. I care. I'm sorry.

43:30.480 --> 43:31.890
