43:37.940 --> 43:40.067
[suspenseful music playing on TV]

43:43.200 --> 43:44.827
-Hey.
-Hey.

43:44.950 --> 43:48.192
-How was the party?
-Stupid party, stupid people.

43:48.290 --> 43:49.575
[laughs]

43:49.660 --> 43:50.991
