43:51.420 --> 43:53.035
Why are you sitting in the dark?

43:53.920 --> 43:56.957
I'm introducing my old man
to the wizarding world of Harry Potter.

43:57.050 --> 43:59.371
-Seriously?
-Seriously.

43:59.800 --> 44:03.042
He's the last person in the world
that doesn't know what his Patronus is.

44:03.510 --> 44:05.751
-Fucking muggles.
-Right?

44:06.430 --> 44:07.306
Hey.

44:08.430 --> 44:11.638
Pay attention here. You're gonna need
to know that for the sixth movie.

44:13.270 --> 44:14.350
Hey, so, uh...

44:16.020 --> 44:17.180
I wanna do Zach next.

44:18.480 --> 44:20.186
Okay. Again?

44:20.280 --> 44:22.942
Yeah. He's just a fucking asshole
who needs to be checked.

44:25.370 --> 44:27.611
-Cool.
-Yeah. So I have this whole idea for him.

44:27.700 --> 44:29.998
-So I'm thinking--
-Ty, you know I'm down for whatever,

44:30.080 --> 44:33.072
but I got to make sure my dad
doesn't fall asleep.

44:33.170 --> 44:35.957
He's, like, 47.
They tend to do that during movies.

44:37.750 --> 44:38.660
Hey.

44:39.710 --> 44:41.211
Just tell me the plan. I'll be there.

44:41.300 --> 44:43.040
Yeah, fine. Later.

44:47.600 --> 44:48.669
[sighs]

45:15.250 --> 45:17.377
[Sonya] Clay, isn't it true
that you heard Hannah say

45:17.460 --> 45:19.246
that she wanted her life to be over?

45:19.340 --> 45:21.160
And isn't it true that you did nothing?

45:22.550 --> 45:24.211
You did nothing to help her.

45:31.010 --> 45:32.978
If he had been honest with us
about the drugs--

45:33.060 --> 45:34.596
Did you know they were gonna ask?

45:35.640 --> 45:39.098
No, of course not. I removed myself, Matt.

45:39.900 --> 45:41.561
If I were to interfere with a witness--

45:41.650 --> 45:43.277
A witness? He's your son.

45:43.360 --> 45:47.399
If I were to interfere in any way,
I would be fired.

45:47.660 --> 45:49.116
I could be disbarred, Matt.

45:49.530 --> 45:50.986
Our boy did drugs, we didn't know.

45:51.080 --> 45:53.150
He hid a homeless boy for a week,
we didn't know.

45:53.250 --> 45:54.569
I mean, what the fuck, Lainie?

45:55.960 --> 45:58.576
-[Lainie] Trying to help a friend in need.
-Our son is in need.

45:58.670 --> 46:00.626
Yes, Matt, I'm aware.

46:01.000 --> 46:04.299
[Clay] I can't stop thinking about it,
Slqe. They destroyed me.

46:04.380 --> 46:05.870
Ask me why she was depressed.

46:06.130 --> 46:08.291
Why she was destroyed.
Ask me who did that to her.

46:08.390 --> 46:10.346
-[Sonya] No further questions.
-[judge] Jury will disregard.

46:10.430 --> 46:11.556
Witness, stand down.

46:12.930 --> 46:14.215
[Clay] But did I deserve it?

46:16.730 --> 46:18.686
[Alex] Who ordered the cinnamon rolls?

46:19.980 --> 46:22.392
IfI put that in my mouth,
I will literally puke.

46:23.230 --> 46:26.199
-Are we, like, all in bad moods?
-[Sheri] I am.

46:26.360 --> 46:29.158
I just don't even have the energy to care.

46:30.070 --> 46:33.483
[Jeff] No, we're just coming down.
It's normal.

46:34.040 --> 46:36.611
-What's the point, right?
-Yeah, exactly.

46:37.870 --> 46:40.168
No, but, like, really,
what's the point of anything?

46:41.210 --> 46:42.700
That's just the Molly talking.

46:44.920 --> 46:46.797
Her name's Hannah.

46:50.510 --> 46:52.887
You've gotta handle the lows
if you wanna chase the highs.

46:54.140 --> 46:57.268
Come on, drink some water.
Don't let your mind go to that dark place.

46:59.730 --> 47:03.518
Do you ever think, "I can't do it
