47:39.270 --> 47:41.181
I've got to be able
to do something to help.

47:44.150 --> 47:46.527
People need to know the whole story.

48:02.920 --> 48:04.035
Hey.

48:04.790 --> 48:07.748
That's great. [scoffs]
That's just perfect.

48:11.550 --> 48:12.369
Clay, honey.

48:17.260 --> 48:20.309
Come on, lover. Give me a little.
I had a shitty day.

48:21.480 --> 48:25.723
